
= "open source" oriented hackers collective

URL = http://hackers4peace.net/

=Manifesto=

"manifesto (draft)

* working for the benefit of all humanity
    
* always keeping in awareness free will of every single human being
    
* acting as a collective of autonomous hackers
    
* establishing web of trust and making heavy use of digital signatures
    
* making all the source code we write publicly available from the very first commit
    
* using only open source software and working towards using only open source hardware
    
* using moneyless budget and strongly supporting money deprecation
    
* publishing attributions of:

 all our direct supporters
 known contributors to the commons which we use
    
* using english language for all source code, documentation and communication within the project
    
* enjoying supporting projects we truly care about!"
(http://hackers4peace.net/manifesto/)


